---
import Layout from "../../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout
  lang="en"
  title="Location | Agua Sala"
  description="How to get to our rural house in Villanueva del Rio y Minas, Seville."
>
  <section class="section-pad">
    <div class="container-site">
      <p class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-wide text-[--color-brand-700]">Location</p>
      <h1 class="mt-2 font-serif text-4xl text-[--color-text] md:text-5xl">Villanueva del Rio y Minas, Seville</h1>
      <p class="mt-6 max-w-3xl text-[--color-text-muted]">
      Our accommodation is in a quiet area with easy access for weekend getaways or long stays. Ideal for disconnecting without giving up proximity to Seville.
      </p>
      <p class="mt-4 max-w-3xl rounded-xl bg-[--color-surface] p-4 text-sm text-[--color-text] ring-1 ring-[--color-border]">
        Exact address: <strong>Avda. Alcalde Victor Mora 9</strong>. Previous reference:
        <strong>Blas Infante 21</strong>.
      </p>

      <div class="mt-10 grid gap-8 lg:grid-cols-[1.05fr_1.45fr]">
        <article class="card-soft p-6">
          <h2 class="font-semibold text-[--color-text]">Orientative distances</h2>
          <ul class="mt-4 space-y-2 text-sm text-[--color-text-muted]">
            <li>Seville capital: approx. 50-60 min</li>
            <li>Munigua site: very close by car</li>
            <li>Natural environment and riverbank: easy access</li>
          </ul>

          <h3 class="mt-6 font-semibold text-[--color-text]">How to get there</h3>
          <p class="mt-3 text-sm text-[--color-text-muted]">
            We will send you exact directions upon confirming the reservation. If you prefer, we attend to you via WhatsApp to facilitate arrival.
          </p>
          <a href="https://wa.me/34620880212" class="btn-primary mt-5">
            Ask for directions
          </a>
        </article>

        <article class="card-soft overflow-hidden p-2">
          <div class="rounded-2xl bg-[--color-brand-50] p-3 text-sm text-[--color-text-muted]">
            Orientative map of the Agua Sala area.
          </div>
          <iframe
            title="Map of location of Agua Sala in Villanueva del Rio y Minas"
            src="https://www.google.com/maps?q=Avda.%20Alcalde%20Victor%20Mora%209%2C%20Villanueva%20del%20Rio%20y%20Minas&output=embed"
            class="mt-2 h-[420px] w-full rounded-2xl"
            loading="lazy"
            referrerpolicy="no-referrer-when-downgrade"
          ></iframe>
        </article>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>